Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.82,0:02:30.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Great Pirate Era...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.81,0:02:37.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...is experiencing a groundswell\Nbeyond the World Government's expectation.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.25,0:02:45.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Being at the center of the unstoppable swell\Nand drawing the most attention is...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.74,0:02:49.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Monkey D. Luffy!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.78,0:02:54.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And the Straw Hats!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.29,0:02:58.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In order to cope with the \Nturbulent Great Pirate Era,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.17,0:03:03.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}50 leaders hold the World Conference\Nevery four years.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.25,0:03:11.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Known as the Reverie, it \Nis now about to start.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.22,0:03:19.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The times are changing drastically now.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.95,0:03:28.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"To the Reverie!\NThe Straw Hats' Sworn Allies Come Together!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.49,0:03:32.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.37,0:03:35.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My bounty has increased \Nbecause of Germa's name...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.75,0:03:41.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't make me happy at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.83,0:03:44.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.09,0:03:47.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do your wounds hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.47,0:03:50.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.09,0:03:52.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.43,0:03:56.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My bounty has decreased!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.56,0:03:59.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look... It's 150 million berries...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.60,0:04:02.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.36,0:04:06.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?! I thought it had increased \Nto 500 million not so long ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.40,0:04:10.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,150 million is lower than\Nyour bounty two years ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.53,0:04:15.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that possible?! Did you do something bad?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.41,0:04:21.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Wouldn't that have increased it?\N--Oh, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.42,0:04:24.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not so bad.\NPeople won't come after you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.46,0:04:29.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami-{\i1}san{\i0}, Luffy is our captain!\NIt could harm our prestige!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.72,0:04:32.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.96,0:04:34.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How are all the royal families?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.87,0:04:35.37,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,NAVY
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.39,0:04:37.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No problems reported!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.52,0:04:38.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about pirates?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.66,0:04:39.17,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,NEW MARINEFORD
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.19,0:04:44.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So far, 13 pirate groups \Nhave attempted to kidnap...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.79,0:04:47.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...royal family members, but we repelled them\Nbefore they approached the ships!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.78,0:04:48.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell the patrol units to \Nstay alert at all times!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.17,0:04:52.39,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,SAKAZUKI - ADMIRAL OF THE FLEET\NNAVY HEADQUARTERS
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.41,0:04:54.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.87,0:04:58.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here to report, Fleet Admiral Sakazuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.08,0:05:00.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Kingdom of Lulucia ship that was en route
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.76,0:05:03.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to the Reverie has been attacked by pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.50,0:05:08.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The king was unharmed\Nbut Princess Comane has been kidnapped...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.67,0:05:10.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did I just tell you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.45,0:05:18.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are guards for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.31,0:05:22.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Check.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.62,0:05:26.32,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,RIKU DOLDO III - THE KING OF DRESSROSA
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.34,0:05:26.46,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ELIZABELLO II - THE KING \NOF THE PRODENCE KINGDOM
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.48,0:05:29.80,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.82,0:05:31.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandfather-{\i1}sama{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.32,0:05:32.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandfather-{\i1}sama{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.57,0:05:35.37,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,--Hm? What's wrong, Rebecca?\N--Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.39,0:05:35.93,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ATTEMPTED ASSASSINATION OF BIG MOM
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.95,0:05:37.08,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you read about Lucy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.10,0:05:38.19,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,REBECCA - LADY-IN-WAITING OF DRESSROSA
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.21,0:05:39.98,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.00,0:05:41.14,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.16,0:05:46.26,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffyland is doing great!\NThat's our boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.28,0:05:46.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The newspaper mentions us, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.94,0:05:51.49,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,LEO - LEADER OF THE TONTA \NCORPS, TONTATTA TRIBE
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.51,0:05:56.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Folks, once we enter the Holyland,\Ndon't talk about such things.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.09,0:05:58.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.18,0:06:01.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're hugely indebted to him but
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.64,0:06:06.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the World Government and the \NNavy see him differently.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.10,0:06:08.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right! He's a pirate!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.36,0:06:13.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not only that but he's also coming to be considered\Na very dangerous man now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.53,0:06:17.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's really something...\NOh yeah! I'll go show this to Viola-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.99,0:06:21.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.87,0:06:24.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's going smoothly...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.56,0:06:24.69,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,VIOLA - PRINCESS OF DRESSROSA
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.71,0:06:29.02,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope we can reach Mariejois \Nwithout a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.04,0:06:29.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.88,0:06:32.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Viola-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.63,0:06:34.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you read about Lucy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.39,0:06:35.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.09,0:06:36.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.47,0:06:44.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It hasn't even been a month since he left Dressrosa\Nbut he is becoming quite a figure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.06,0:06:47.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.40,0:06:51.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no mistake... Those are ships of\NDressrosa and Prodence Kingdom!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.96,0:06:54.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No Navy guards!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.32,0:06:57.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! I-I see Princess Viola!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.61,0:07:00.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She is as gorgeous as they say.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.15,0:07:02.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The girl she's with is also \Na royal family member?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.49,0:07:07.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we kidnap them,\NI wonder how much they'll pay us!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.54,0:07:10.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think, Princess Comane?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.98,0:07:17.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Contact my daddy already!\NHe'll pay you as much as you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.76,0:07:19.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is why I like royal families!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.97,0:07:23.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you gotta wait a little.\NWe're greedy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.77,0:07:28.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll never notice us because...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.35,0:07:31.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...we're hiding underwater!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.27,0:07:35.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Sink them!\N--Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.44,0:07:43.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's impossible to guard against a torpedo!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.22,0:08:01.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.89,0:08:03.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An enemy attack?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.81,0:08:07.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Get the cannons ready!\N--Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.81,0:08:13.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Don't worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.94,0:08:17.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad that I made it. You're safe now!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.24,0:08:17.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Are you a Navy soldier?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.26,0:08:20.16,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,JUSTICE
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.18,0:08:20.64,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,KOBY - CAPTAIN OF THE NAVY HEADQUARTERS
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.66,0:08:24.35,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Koby, a captain of the Navy Headquarters!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.37,0:08:30.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Did it miss the target?!\N--No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.71,0:08:33.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna sink!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.00,0:08:38.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not hurt, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.59,0:08:43.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're parties from Dressrosa and Prodence.\NYou must be tired from your long journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.68,0:08:51.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What just happened?\NHow did you get here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.23,0:08:55.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got here from a distant Navy ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.36,0:08:59.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This ship was just targeted \Nfrom under the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.82,0:09:03.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Under the sea... You mean by a torpedo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.28,0:09:05.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad they missed...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.28,0:09:08.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.12,0:09:10.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Helmeppo-{\i1}san{\i0}, how's it over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.79,0:09:17.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We caught the pirates!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.25,0:09:18.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.44,0:09:18.44,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,HELMEPPO\NLIEUTENANT COMMANDER OF THE NAVY HEADQUARTERS
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.46,0:09:21.66,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess Comane from Lulucia is okay, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.68,0:09:26.54,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,You little...! Roast these jerks on a skewer!\NI won't forgive them!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.56,0:09:29.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, they'll get the \Nharshest punishment, princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.39,0:09:34.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, what's wrong with your Color of Observation,\NKoby?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.48,0:09:40.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't feel a torpedo anywhere at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.23,0:09:41.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A submarine...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.67,0:09:46.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to be careful with pirates these days...\NThat was close.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.11,0:09:48.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.70,0:09:51.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're the famous Captain Koby!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.25,0:09:54.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? From the Rocky Port Incident?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.62,0:10:00.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The incident was masterminded by Trafalgar Law,\None of the Worst Generation...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.88,0:10:06.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the hero who protected the citizens\Nat that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.18,0:10:08.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, I'm not a hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.89,0:10:12.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not just a daring guy\Nbut also a fine young man!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.10,0:10:15.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wow... This man must be strong...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.35,0:10:19.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He doesn't even hold saving us\Nfrom the torpedo over our heads...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.19,0:10:20.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.53,0:10:22.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.30,0:10:24.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Luffy-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.24,0:10:29.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, it's Straw Hat Luffy!\NThe front-page article caught my eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.24,0:10:30.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you wanna read it, Koby-{\i1}san{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.87,0:10:38.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no. Well, I mean, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.08,0:10:41.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"A great captain with 5,000 subordinates"...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.50,0:10:44.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"Destroyed Big Mom's castle"...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.51,0:10:48.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"Took down the top officer \Nwho is worth a billion"...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.26,0:10:51.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"The fifth Emperor of the Sea"...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.60,0:10:56.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Luffy-san's as cool as always!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.44,0:10:59.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He keeps moving forward!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.73,0:11:06.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Koby-{\i1}san{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.07,0:11:14.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Every time I see you in the newspaper,\NI think of that day...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.25,0:11:30.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I slept great!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.14,0:11:34.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you toying with us\Neven when you know we're pirates?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.43,0:11:36.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, I'm hungry! You got any food?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.67,0:11:38.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen when people are talking!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.10,0:11:41.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You damn kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.02,0:11:49.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.66,0:11:56.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the big idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.91,0:11:59.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--W-Who {\i1}are{\i0} you?!\N--Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.67,0:12:03.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Monkey D. Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.75,0:12:11.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That day, I got in a boat\Non the outskirts of town to go fishing...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.30,0:12:17.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it turned out the boat was\Nactually headed for a pirate ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.89,0:12:19.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been two years since...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.39,0:12:23.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In exchange for my life, I've \Nbeen forced to be a chore boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.63,0:12:25.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, you're dumb and stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.78,0:12:27.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're brutally honest...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.90,0:12:30.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't like it, then run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.12,0:12:32.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I can't! No way! No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.18,0:12:35.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just the thought of Alvida-{\i1}sama{\i0} finding me\Nfrightens me and
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.82,0:12:37.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,makes my knees knock together!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.41,0:12:40.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're a wimp, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.71,0:12:44.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, I hate you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.50,0:12:47.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.44,0:12:52.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If only I had the courage\Nto drift the ocean in a barrel,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.07,0:12:55.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there's actually something \NI want to do, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.25,0:12:56.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.31,0:13:02.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm... What compelled you\Nto set out onto the sea, Luffy-{\i1}san{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.85,0:13:05.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.40,0:13:13.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,K-K-King of the Pirates?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.89,0:13:45.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}K-K-King of the Pirates?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.42,0:13:47.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,K... K...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.58,0:13:53.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,K-King of the Pirates is the title given to the person\Nwho obtains everything in this world!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.32,0:14:00.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That means seeking the great treasure of wealth,\Nfame, and power... the One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.26,0:14:02.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Yup!\N--Yup?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.08,0:14:05.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pirates all over the world \Nare after that treasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.00,0:14:07.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.13,0:14:11.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! No way, no way, no way!\NAbsolutely no way!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.73,0:14:17.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way you can stand at\Nthe apex of this Great Pirate Era! No way! No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.86,0:14:20.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you hit me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.02,0:14:23.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just because.\NIt's not about whether I can or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.44,0:14:24.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.56,0:14:28.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna do it because I want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.23,0:14:35.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've decided to be the King of the Pirates,\Nso if I die fighting for that,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.49,0:14:41.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that's fine with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.41,0:14:44.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Do you suppose I can do it, too?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.16,0:14:46.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}--If I'm prepared to die for it?\N--Do what?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.96,0:14:50.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think even I could join the Navy?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.34,0:14:51.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Navy?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.51,0:14:56.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Catching bad guys is my dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.08,0:14:57.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think I can do it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.58,0:14:58.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How should I know?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.98,0:15:02.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! I'll do it! If I'm gonna be a chore boy\Nfor the rest of my life,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.84,0:15:04.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then I'll break out of here
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.52,0:15:09.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and catch even Alvida-{\i1}sama{\i0}... no, Alvida!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.36,0:15:12.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--L-Luffy-{\i1}san{\i0}! Let's get out of here!\N--Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.36,0:15:14.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You saw how powerful her club is!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.82,0:15:19.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In these waters, she's the most...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.16,0:15:21.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the most what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.66,0:15:24.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Th-The...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.83,0:15:30.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The most ugly, cragged old hag ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.50,0:15:32.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.21,0:15:37.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I'm going to join the Navy!\NAnd then I'm gonna beat up pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.34,0:15:40.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you even know what you're saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.30,0:15:44.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I do! I'm gonna do what I want to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.35,0:15:47.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna... I'm gonna join the Navy...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.26,0:15:50.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And catch your lousy ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.19,0:15:54.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You damn pipsqueak!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.07,0:15:58.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's how Luffy-{\i0}san{\i1} and \NI went out on a journey.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.49,0:16:02.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stand to watch the \NNavy like this anymore! I...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.11,0:16:06.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...want to be an honorable Navy soldier!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.91,0:16:08.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so wrong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.39,0:16:13.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy-{\i1}san{\i0} and I haven't known each \Nother long, but we {\i1}are{\i0} friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.63,0:16:14.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.42,0:16:20.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! We're gonna part ways,\Nbut we'll always be friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.47,0:16:25.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.31,0:16:28.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it true that you are pirates?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.23,0:16:33.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. We gained a member\Nand became a pirate group just now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.88,0:16:40.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We appreciate that you saved our base\Nand this town from that tyrant!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.53,0:16:42.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.03,0:16:44.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,now that we know you are pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.45,0:16:48.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in the name of the Navy, \Nwe cannot stand by quietly!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.75,0:16:51.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You will leave this town at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.83,0:16:56.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Out of obligation,\Nwe will refrain from contacting headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.25,0:16:58.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, guess we should go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.28,0:17:06.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for the food, lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.67,0:17:08.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you part of their crew?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.56,0:17:10.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.31,0:17:14.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.96,0:17:16.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.16,0:17:18.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well? Is he?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.78,0:17:23.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know what he's done until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.78,0:17:25.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Luffy-{\i0}san{\i1}! You wouldn't!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.96,0:17:30.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was this reaaally fat pirate lady,\NI think her name was Ahiruda.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.54,0:17:32.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.13,0:17:36.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If they find out I was on a pirate ship,\NI'll never get to join the Navy!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.34,0:17:40.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, she was an ugly hag!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.05,0:17:44.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And for two whole years, this guy was her--
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.05,0:17:51.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Please don't! Please don't!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.64,0:17:53.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now you've done it, you bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.85,0:17:56.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you! Damn you! Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.92,0:17:58.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.61,0:18:05.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! You've gone too far. That's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.24,0:18:08.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's very clear that you \Nguys aren't crewmates!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.72,0:18:16.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now leave this town at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.09,0:18:19.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}On purpose...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.59,0:18:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He did that on purpose...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.68,0:18:25.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For me...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.63,0:18:33.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He purposely got me riled up\Nto make me hit him...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.44,0:18:41.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Please! Please!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.11,0:18:46.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me join the Navy!\NI'll gladly do chores or anything else!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.42,0:18:50.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it means I can be a Navy soldier!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.95,0:18:53.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Commander! I'm against the idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.80,0:18:56.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I still don't fully trust this kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.62,0:18:59.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There {\i1}have{\i0} been cases of Navy \Nsoldiers being pirate spies!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.00,0:19:03.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll first need to conduct \Na background check...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.15,0:19:11.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a man who will become a Navy officer!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.43,0:19:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!\NI'll never forget all you've done for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.02,0:19:22.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never heard of\Na pirate being thanked by a Navy soldier.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.73,0:19:25.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's meet again sometime, Koby!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.40,0:19:26.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy-{\i1}san{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.57,0:19:28.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All hands, salute!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.91,0:19:36.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.16,0:19:42.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Captain Koby! What are you doing?\NCome back!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.71,0:19:48.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.34,0:19:51.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.10,0:19:52.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.84,0:19:56.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, you'll soon arrive at New Marineford,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.37,0:20:00.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so we'll escort you from here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.98,0:20:03.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.69,0:20:06.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.49,0:20:07.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.70,0:20:09.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you like Lucy, Koby-{\i1}kun{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.70,0:20:11.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You like Luffyland, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.98,0:20:14.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! H-He's our enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.33,0:20:16.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.50,0:20:18.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We won't tell anyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.26,0:20:20.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's have a chat.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.04,0:20:23.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L-Let go of me! I-I'm from the Navy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.79,0:20:26.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you looked happy\Nwhen you were reading the paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.56,0:20:29.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Th-That's because...\N--Come on. Let's talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.45,0:20:31.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,P-Please stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.26,0:20:34.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Luffyland is in this article here, too!
